body: Can you please try using **tf-nightly** version? Also please take a look at documentation to [convert a keras .h5 file into tf lite](https://www.tensorflow.org/lite/convert/python_api#exporting_a_tfkeras_file_) and [additional instructions](https://www.tensorflow.org/lite/convert/python_api#converting_models_in_tensorflow_19_to_tensorflow_111_) if you haven't already.
